serve as U.S. ambassador to both New Zealand and Western Samoa. She
would succeed Paul Matthews Cleveland.
   Ms. Newman is president of Village Real Estate in Seattle. She
was Washington state chairman for Bush's 1988 presidential campaign
and a co-chair of the Reagan-Bush Finance Committee in 1984.
