<TEXT>
   Share prices closed sharply lower Thursday on the
London Stock Exchange following a steep drop in the afternoon.
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index fell 22.3
points, or 1.1 percent, to 2,049.4.
   Volume rose to 525.4 million shares from 449.8 million shares on
