airports, took delivery Thursday of the first two of of the eight
MD-87 planes it ordered last year, the company said.
   Delivery of the new order of MD-82s is set to begin in late 1993
and run through 1997.
   The two models of plane are similar in design. The MD-82 can
carry up to 172 passengers and the MD-87 can be configured to carry
a maximum of 139.
